data.description: $1500 SELLER CONCESSION WITH ACCEPTED OFFER ** Assumable mortgage at 4.875% available to qualifying buyers (Monthly Payment is currently $1500). Majestic Oaks- in the heart of SW Ocala presents this charming 3BR/2BA home with a spacious Florida room, offering 1,887 soft of beautifully renovated living space. Enjoy modern living with new kitchen cabinets, granite countertops, and luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout. The roof was replaced in 2023, HVAC in 2015, drain field in 2020. The property features fresh interior and exterior paint and a serene park-like backyard with mature landscaping and concrete curbing. This turnkey gem is a must-see, providing a perfect blend of style and comfort in a desirable SW Ocala neighborhood close to everything. Contact today for your own private tour.
